        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2018-04-05 18:25:24.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n(3 comments)\n\nNing, Please find my reply in comments.\n\n1. I suggest you to brush-up TPM, its interfaces, tpm2-abrmd, IBM emulator etc. This will help us to avoid questions in those areas.\n\n2. To reply to one of your comment, we are using following stack versions\ntpm2-tss  : 1.2.0\ntp2-abrmd : 1.1.1\ntpm2-tools: 2.1.0\n\nThe tool works in the above mentioned tag versions and tested.\n\nWe can commit the existing changes as we have a tool which works on the mentioned tag versions.\nIf someone wants to upgrade the tool to latest version, they can do so. \nOr I can update this tool to latest versions of tpm2-stack little later but not sure of when I can do it.",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
